contributingText1: We've heard your requests and are __actively__ developing an extensive **Beginner's Guide**. Our goal is to create a resource that teaches developers _common practices_, _core concepts_, and most of all, how to actually use **Vuetify**.
contributingText2: Join the conversation in our [Community](https://community.vuetifyjs.com) with your questions and feedback.
